let's set a date.

815
00:54:44,573 --> 00:54:47,158
Well, how about next Friday?

816
00:54:47,159 --> 00:54:48,576
- That works.
- Sounds good.

817
00:54:48,577 --> 00:54:49,828
It works for me.

818
00:54:50,829 --> 00:54:52,788
- But it won't work for Huiji.
- Really?

819
00:54:52,789 --> 00:54:55,291
- And how do you know this?
- She just has things to do.

820
00:54:55,292 --> 00:54:57,210
Because of that CCTV footage?

821
00:54:57,211 --> 00:54:58,462
She's done with that.

822
00:54:59,630 --> 00:55:02,882
- But she just has things to do.
- Okay, how about tonight then?

823
00:55:02,883 --> 00:55:04,800
- Tonight sounds good too.
- Me too.

824
00:55:04,801 --> 00:55:06,928
- Tonight won't work either.
- You or Huiji?

825
00:55:06,929 --> 00:55:09,723
- Both of us.
- Geez, when can we hang out then?

826
00:55:12,059 --> 00:55:14,561
Hey, you said you had a trial. Go on.

827
00:55:15,229 --> 00:55:17,271
- Okay.
- I'll put up a poll in the group text.

828
00:55:17,272 --> 00:55:18,356
What case is this?

829
