This is Munjeong's case.
I was helping out for 10,000 won.

830
00:55:21,652 --> 00:55:23,779
Hey! I said that's for Huiji!

831
00:55:25,864 --> 00:55:27,282
What's his deal?

832
00:55:28,200 --> 00:55:29,659
Geez, I can't do this.

833
00:55:29,660 --> 00:55:33,412
Munjeong, take this back.
I can't do this for just 10,000 won.

834
00:55:33,413 --> 00:55:34,497
Why not, Attorney Ha?

835
00:55:34,498 --> 00:55:37,166
A 150-page summary
for 10,000 won is ridiculous.

836
00:55:37,167 --> 00:55:40,127
- No refunds.
- Give me another 10,000 won, please.

837
00:55:40,128 --> 00:55:42,255
- Just 10,000 won more.
- Just have some <i>kimbap.</i>

838
00:55:42,256 --> 00:55:43,840
Just an extra 10,000 won!

839
00:55:59,439 --> 00:56:00,439
Hello, Mr. Na.

840
00:56:00,440 --> 00:56:02,984
<i>- You're not in court today, right?</i>
- That's right.

841
00:56:02,985 --> 00:56:05,778
I just got a call that my kid's hurt,
so I rushed out.

842
00:56:05,779 --> 00:56:08,322
But I totally forgot
that I had a trial to attend.

843
00:56:08,323 --> 00:56:10,825
Could you cover for me?

844
00:56:10,826 --> 00:56:12,285
<i>Okay, sir.</i>

845
00:56:12,286 --> 00:56:13,537
