848
00:56:19,585 --> 00:56:21,502
If you run, you'll make it in time.

849
00:56:21,503 --> 00:56:24,463
Okay, I'll hang up now.

850
00:56:24,464 --> 00:56:25,757
<i>All right. Sorry.</i>

851
00:56:28,427 --> 00:56:29,553
Damn it.

852
00:56:33,098 --> 00:56:34,099
Damn it!

853
00:56:34,891 --> 00:56:36,434
Attorney Bae!

854
00:56:36,435 --> 00:56:38,937
Thank you! Sorry!

855
00:56:58,081 --> 00:57:00,959
The plaintiff, Pungcheon Trading Company.
Are you present?

856
