I'll cut to the chase.

947
01:03:11,955 --> 01:03:14,708
I'd like to ask you to take a case.

948
01:03:17,502 --> 01:03:19,461
It's not a case that I'm involved in.

949
01:03:19,462 --> 01:03:22,132
It's just a referral,
so please don't feel pressured.

950
01:03:24,843 --> 01:03:25,968
Take on a case?

951
01:03:25,969 --> 01:03:27,053
Yes.

952
01:03:27,721 --> 01:03:29,930
Out of this group,

953
01:03:29,931 --> 01:03:32,434
